DTSTAMP;TZID=UTC:20240708T185423
LAST-MODIFIED;TZID=UTC:20241001T162706
SUMMARY:October Campout
DESCRIPTION: Join us for our first campout of the year. We will be on 
 church property and have access to the bathrooms only. Come prepared for 
 the cold nights with your sleeping bags and extra blankets. We will only 
 have a snack Friday no dinner so make sure to eat before you arrive. Drop 
 off at 6pm and pick up at 4 pm Saturday. Cost is $10 per person adult and 
 Kid. You must be a registered adult member to participate. All 
 tenderhearts require a parent to accompany them on overnights. 
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC ""-//W3C//DTD HTML 3.2//EN""><BODY><p>Join us for our first campout of the year.</p><p>We will be on church property and have access to the bathrooms only.</p><p>Come prepared for the cold nights with your sleeping bags and extra blankets.</p><p><br /></p><p>We will only have a snack Friday no dinner so make sure to eat before you arrive.</p><p>Drop off at 6pm and pick up at 4 pm Saturday. </p><p>Cost is $10 per person adult and Kid. </p><p>You must be a registered adult member to participate. All tenderhearts require a parent to accompany them on overnights.</p><p><br /></p></BODY></HTML>
