DTSTAMP;TZID=UTC:20241021T170826
LAST-MODIFIED;TZID=UTC:20241028T131403
SUMMARY:PiPa Self defense class
DESCRIPTION: This event is a required step for the Emergency Preparedness 
 that is our 3rd badge we will be working on this year. This is 
 requirement 2 on page 210 in your handbook. We will be meeting at the 
 location in Victor for this class. It is scheduled to start before our 
 meeting time so that you will have time to transport to and from and 
 still make it to the meeting in Henrietta for your other family members. 
 Because this class costs a larger amount than we normally spend on 
 badgework, and this is just one step, we are asking that each girl pay 
 for a part of the fee for the class. This will be $7 per girl. The troop 
 is covering the rest of the cost from the dues for badgework. Please make 
 payment to Debbie at sign in for this event. The release form from Gracie 
 will need to be signed by parents before the girls can participate. Here 
 is the link to the form. https://sparkpages.io/forms/?frm=_cJt Please 
 make sure this is completed before dropping off on the 4th. 
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC ""-//W3C//DTD HTML 3.2//EN""><BODY><p>This event is a required step for the Emergency Preparedness that is our 3rd badge we will be working on this year. This is requirement 2 on page 210 in your handbook. We will be meeting at the location in Victor for this class. It is scheduled to start before our meeting time so that you will have time to transport to and from and still make it to the meeting in Henrietta for your other family members. Because this class costs a larger amount than we normally spend on badgework, and this is just one step, we are asking that each girl pay for a part of the fee for the class. This will be $7 per girl. The troop is covering the rest of the cost from the dues for badgework. </p><p>Please make payment to Debbie at sign in for this event. </p><p>The release form from Gracie will need to be signed by parents before the girls can participate. Here is the link to the form. <a href="https://sparkpages.io/forms/?frm=_cJt">https://sparkpages.io/forms/?frm=_cJt</a> Please make sure this is completed before dropping off on the 4th.</p></BODY></HTML>
