UID:AHGFAMILY-evyqagegfg8o-20240708T194649
DTSTAMP;TZID=UTC:20240708T191031
LAST-MODIFIED;TZID=UTC:20240708T194649
SUMMARY:Caroling
DESCRIPTION: Join us to carol for the church neighbors. We will meet at 
 the church and walk down the street next to the church caroling to those 
 who open their doors for us. We have a lot of fun with this meeting each 
 year and always hear wonderful responses from the community afterwards. 
 Help us spread the holiday cheer. Parents and other family members are 
 welcome to join us if they would like. Just a heads up we will be 
 splitting up from the Trail life boys as our troops are to big to carol 
 together. So keep that in mind if you have kids in both groups. you will 
 have to choose one to go with. 
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC ""-//W3C//DTD HTML 3.2//EN""><BODY><p>Join us to carol for the church neighbors. We will meet at the church and walk down the street next to the church caroling to those who open their doors for us. We have a lot of fun with this meeting each year and always hear wonderful responses from the community afterwards. </p><p>Help us spread the holiday cheer.</p><p>Parents and other family members are welcome to join us if they would like. Just a heads up we will be splitting up from the Trail life boys as our troops are to big to carol together. So keep that in mind if you have kids in both groups. you will have to choose one to go with. </p></BODY></HTML>
