SUMMARY:Ceremony and Christmas Party
DESCRIPTION: We will be having an awards ceremony and our Christmas party 
 all in one. Joining awards will be handed out at this time as well as 
 anything earned over the summer. Then we will have the girls play a game 
 to exchange gifts. Please bring a $5 gift to exchange that would be good 
 for your daughters level to exchange. Wrapped and without a tag. This 
 gift takes place your your dues for December. 
