SUMMARY:Canceled  Cabin Campout
DESCRIPTION: Join us for a fun weekend away this winter. There are 26 
 bunks, but there is also lots of space for anyone who would like to join 
 us on an air mattress or cot of your own. The cost per person, parents 
 included is $25. This covers food and the cabin fee for the weekend. This 
 amount will be due by the 24th so that I can buy the food we need before 
 the campout. Bring your bible a thin air mattress or thick camping pad. 
 (the bunk beds do not have mattresses) there is space for full size air 
 mattresses on the floor if you don't have a thin one to fit on the beds. 
 bedding (sleeping bag and blankets, pillow and air mattress or cot if you 
 would prefer. Pjs and cloths for the weekend. Extra socks and outdoor 
 cloths in case we have space to have some outdoor fun on sat. Extra 
 cloths in case we get wet while outside. Bathroom supplies would just be 
 toothbrushes and hair brushes as there is no shower. If your daughter has 
 any medications required over the weekend, please let me know ahead of 
 time and then leave them with me before you leave when dropping them off. 
 Reminder that Tenderhearts require an adult member parent to accompany 
 them on overnights. Drop off time is 6pm Friday night. and Pick up will 
 be 10 am Sunday morning. 
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC ""-//W3C//DTD HTML 3.2//EN""><BODY><p>Join us for a fun weekend away this winter.</p><p>There are 26 bunks, but there is also lots of space for anyone who would like to join us on an air mattress or cot of your own.</p><p>The cost per person, parents included is $25. This covers food and the cabin fee for the weekend. This amount will be due by the 24th so that I can buy the food we need before the campout.</p><p>Bring your bible</p><p>a thin air mattress or thick camping pad. (the bunk beds do not have mattresses) there is space for full size air mattresses on the floor if you don't have a thin one to fit on the beds.</p><p>bedding (sleeping bag and blankets, pillow and air mattress or cot if you would prefer.</p><p>Pjs and cloths for the weekend. Extra socks and outdoor cloths in case we have space to have some outdoor fun on sat.</p><p>Extra cloths in case we get wet while outside.</p><p>Bathroom supplies would just be toothbrushes and hair brushes as there is no shower.</p><p>If your daughter has any medications required over the weekend, please let me know ahead of time and then leave them with me before you leave when dropping them off.</p><p>Reminder that Tenderhearts require an adult member parent to accompany them on overnights.</p><p>Drop off time is 6pm Friday night. and Pick up will be 10 am Sunday morning.</p><p><br /></p></BODY></HTML>
