SUMMARY:Derby Build Day
DESCRIPTION: ***** PLEASE NOTE: THIS IS NOT A DROP OFF EVENT! DUE TO 
 LIMITED SUPERVISION AND THE DANGERS OF USING TOOLS, A PARENT/GUARDIAN IS 
 REQUIRED TO ACCOMPANY EACH YOUTH PARTICIPANT ***** Join us anytime 
 between 1-4 to work on your Derby car. Bring your car, at whatever stage 
 of the build you're at, and work on it with us. If you don't have a car 
 kit yet, they will be available to purchase for $5 each for the basic 
 block or wedge. We will also have pre-shaped cars available this year for 
 $8 each. We will have many tools available to help in your build. Come 
 ask questions, get advice on how to make your car run faster and 
 straighter, and get the help you need to complete your Derby car. Bring 
 your design ideas and we will help you bring them to life. We will have 
 leaders available to assist with your build, but we don't have enough 
 leaders to work one-on-one with everyone. Parents, please plan to stay 
 and help your daughter. Registered racers who's cars don't meet our 
 official rules will be entered into the "Outlaw" class. They will still 
 be allowed to race, but will not qualify for a trophy. Our official rules 
 are attached below. NY2911 Timber Derby Official Rules Here is a 
 printable sheet to help you draw out your design. Be advised, this 
 template is not an exact size match and is only meant as a design aid. 
 Derby car blank template.pdf 
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC ""-//W3C//DTD HTML 3.2//EN""><BODY><p>***** PLEASE NOTE: THIS IS NOT A DROP OFF EVENT! DUE TO LIMITED SUPERVISION AND THE DANGERS OF USING TOOLS, A PARENT/GUARDIAN IS REQUIRED TO ACCOMPANY EACH YOUTH PARTICIPANT *****<br /></p><p>Join us anytime between 1-4 to work on your Derby car. Bring your car, at whatever stage of the build you're at, and work on it with us. If you don't have a car kit yet, they will be available to purchase for $5 each for the basic block or wedge. We will also have pre-shaped cars available this year for $8 each. We will have many tools available to help in your build. Come ask questions, get advice on how to make your car run faster and straighter, and get the help you need to complete your Derby car. Bring your design ideas and we will help you bring them to life. We will have leaders available to assist with your build, but we don't have enough leaders to work one-on-one with everyone. Parents, please plan to stay and help your daughter.</p><p>Registered racers who's cars don't meet our official rules will be entered into the "Outlaw" class. They will still be allowed to race, but will not qualify for a trophy.</p><p>Our official rules are attached below.</p><p><a href="https://www.ahgfamily.org/getdoc/doceffjhmyiu">NY2911 Timber Derby Official Rules</a></p><p>Here is a printable sheet to help you draw out your design. Be advised, this template is not an <em>exact</em> size match and is only meant as a design aid.</p><p><a href="https://www.ahgfamily.org/getdoc/dockedflzlw3">Derby car blank template.pdf</a></p></BODY></HTML>
