LAST-MODIFIED;TZID=UTC:20250727T235016
SUMMARY:Full troop Campout @ Letchworth State Park
DESCRIPTION: Join us for a full troop campout @ Letchworth State Park. 
 More information to come. We have changed up the summer plans because of 
 my foot injury and are now looking forward to a full troop campout 
 instead of a pipa only campout. Join us for some end of summer fun! Cost 
 for the campsite is $5 per person, Cost of food for the weekend is $25 
 per person so total cost per person is $30 for this campout. I will be at 
 the church on the 28th of July for a meeting downstairs from 6pm-8pm if 
 you would like to pay cash. Otherwise you can mail me a check. please 
 text me for my address my phone number is 585-489-4870. Things to pack... 
 Sleeping bag/ bedding/ air mattress/ pillow Extra blankets or sheets 
 incase Cloths for 3 days rain gear sneakers Mess kit towel (incase 
 anything gets wet/ you included) Flash light Toothbrush/ toothpaste/ hair 
 brush Camping chair Bug spray Bible Follow the link below to the 
 campsite. Enter after 5pm to avoid the vehicle entrance fee. 
 https://maps.app.goo.gl/8nxTV6tdHrA5dNV56 
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC ""-//W3C//DTD HTML 3.2//EN""><BODY><p>Join us for a full troop campout @ Letchworth State Park. More information to come.</p><p>We have changed up the summer plans because of my foot injury and are now looking forward to a full troop campout instead of a pipa only campout.</p><p>Join us for some end of summer fun!</p><p>Cost for the campsite is $5 per person, Cost of food for the weekend is $25 per person so total cost per person is $30 for this campout.</p><p>I will be at the church on the 28th of July for a meeting downstairs from 6pm-8pm if you would like to pay cash. Otherwise you can mail me a check. please text me for my address my phone number is 585-489-4870.</p><p>Things to pack...</p><ul><li>Sleeping bag/ bedding/ air mattress/ pillow</li><li>Extra blankets or sheets incase</li><li>Cloths for 3 days</li><li>rain gear</li><li>sneakers</li><li>Mess kit</li><li>towel (incase anything gets wet/ you included) </li><li>Flash light</li><li>Toothbrush/ toothpaste/ hair brush</li><li>Camping chair</li><li>Bug spray</li><li>Bible</li></ul><p><strong>Follow the link below to the campsite. Enter after 5pm to avoid the vehicle entrance fee.</strong><br /></p><p><span class="redactor-invisible-space"><a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/8nxTV6tdHrA5dNV56">https://maps.app.goo.gl/8nxTV6tdHrA5dNV56</a></span><br /></p></BODY></HTML>
