SUMMARY:Mother Daughter Event
DESCRIPTION: Join us for a fun time together as mom and daughter, We will 
 be making flower arrangements together that you can take home. One 
 arrangement per family. the cost for this due to the supplies is $10 per 
 family. Payments can be made on Zeffy with this link 
 https://www.zeffy.com/en-US/ticketing/ahg-mother-d... or with Amy at drop 
 off. Please Bring a snack to share while we craft. No nuts, seeds or 
 humus. Here is a link to sign up to help before or after the event 
 https://www.signupgenius.com/go/10C0F4FAEAC2CAAFAC... Please let us know 
 if you can make it ASAP so we can make sure to have the correct amount of 
 supplies for you ahead of time. 
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC ""-//W3C//DTD HTML 3.2//EN""><BODY><p>Join us for a fun time together as mom and daughter,</p><p>We will be making flower arrangements together that you can take home.</p><p>One arrangement per family. the cost for this due to the supplies is <strong>$10 per family. Payments can be made on Zeffy with this link <span class="redactor-invisible-space"><a href="https://www.zeffy.com/en-US/ticketing/ahg-mother-daughter-event">https://www.zeffy.com/en-US/ticketing/ahg-mother-d...</a></span> or with Amy at drop off.</strong></p><p><strong>Please Bring a snack to share while we craft. No nuts, seeds or humus.</strong></p><p>Here is a link to sign up to help before or after the event <span class="redactor-invisible-space"><a href="https://www.signupgenius.com/go/10C0F4FAEAC2CAAFACE9-60199701-ahgmother">https://www.signupgenius.com/go/10C0F4FAEAC2CAAFAC...</a></span></p><p>Please let us know if you can make it ASAP so we can make sure to have the correct amount of supplies for you ahead of time.</p><p><br /></p></BODY></HTML>
