 toothpaste/ hair brush change of cloths pillows 
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC ""-//W3C//DTD HTML 3.2//EN""><BODY><p>We will be spending the night at the church having some with games and a bible study.</p> <p><b>Please bring a snack to share for the Friday night fun</b>.</p> <p>Tenderhearts require a parent AHG Member to be present for all sleepovers</p> <p>Cost is $5 per person for breakfast supplies. Payment can be made through Zeffy with this link <a href="https://www.zeffy.com/en-US/ticketing/lock-in-jan-full-troop" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">zeffy.com/en-US/ticketing/lock-in-jan-full-troop , <span style="color:#000000;">or by cash or check at sign in time.</span></a></p> <p>Bring</p> <p>Air mattress- camping cot</p> <p>Sleeping bag</p> <p>Toothbrush and toothpaste/ hair brush</p> <p>change of cloths</p> <p>pillows</p></BODY></HTML>
