DTSTAMP;TZID=UTC:20250729T141306
LAST-MODIFIED;TZID=UTC:20260225T165139
SUMMARY:Cabin Campout at Camp Hickory Hill
DESCRIPTION: Join us for a fun weekend at camp Hickory Hill. Tenderhearts 
 require a Parent Adult member to be present for all overnights. We will 
 be working on some badgework but also having fun playing in the gym. The 
 badgework we will be working on will be a part of the Explorers troop 
 badgework for this year. This means if you have an Explorer and they can 
 not make it to this campout you will need to make up this work on your 
 own to earn this badge. Cost is $50 per person. you can pay through zeffy 
 with this link  
 zeffy.com/en-US/ticketing/feb-cabin-campout-at-camp-hickory-hill  or by 
 cash or check at sign in time. This payment is due by Feb 16th. Things to 
 bring sleeping bag/ pillow/ extra blankets Cloths for the weather ( we 
 will be outside for different parts of the day) Toiletries (there are 
 showers) Mess kit refillable bottle for water throughout the day 
 flashlight coat / hat/ gloves/ winter boots Please also bring a second 
 pair of sneakers as we can only use clean shoes on the carpeted gym floor 
 for when we are playing games.  
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC ""-//W3C//DTD HTML 3.2//EN""><BODY><p>Join us for a fun weekend at camp Hickory Hill.</p> <p>Tenderhearts require a Parent Adult member to be present for all overnights.</p> <p>We will be working on some badgework but also having fun playing in the gym. </p> <p><b>The badgework we will be working on will be a part of the Explorers troop badgework for this year. This means if you have an Explorer and they can not make it to this campout you will need to make up this work on your own to earn this badge.</b></p> <p>Cost is $50 per person. you can pay through zeffy with this link <a href="https://www.zeffy.com/en-US/ticketing/feb-cabin-campout-at-camp-hickory-hill" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">zeffy.com/en-US/ticketing/feb-cabin-campout-at-camp-hickory-hill  <span style="color:#000000;">or by cash or check at sign in time.</span></a></p> <p><span style="color:#000000;">This payment is due by Feb 16th.</span></p> <p>Things to bring</p> <p>sleeping bag/ pillow/ extra blankets</p> <p>Cloths for the weather ( we will be outside for different parts of the day)</p> <p>Toiletries (there are showers)</p> <p>Mess kit</p> <p><b>refillable bottle for water </b>throughout the day</p> <p>flashlight</p> <p>coat / hat/ gloves/ winter boots</p> <p>Please also bring a <b>second pair of sneakers</b> as we can only use clean shoes on the carpeted gym floor for when we are playing games. </p> <p></p></BODY></HTML>
