SUMMARY:End of year Ceremony
DESCRIPTION: Please make sure to arrive early so we can start on time as 
 there is alot to get through for both troops. Be in full uniform We start 
 at 6pm instead of 6:30 so please arrive by 5:45 Please bring a snack to 
 shar as well for after the ceremony for a time of fellowship and 
 celebration of what the girls earned- Nut and seed free as well as 
 labeled for those with other allergies 
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC ""-//W3C//DTD HTML 3.2//EN""><BODY><p>Please make sure to arrive early so we can start on time as there is alot to get through for both troops.</p><p>Be in full uniform</p><p>We start at 6pm instead of 6:30 so please arrive by 5:45</p><p>Please bring a snack to shar as well for after the ceremony for a time of fellowship and celebration of what the girls earned- Nut and seed free as well as labeled for those with other allergies</p></BODY></HTML>
