LAST-MODIFIED;TZID=UTC:20260527T143821
SUMMARY:Campout
DESCRIPTION: Join us for a campout Place to be determined Tenderhearts 
 Require an Parent adult member to be present for all overnights Here is 
 the link for Payment on Zeffy. 
 zeffy.com/en-US/ticketing/june-campout--2026 Payments are due by June 
 5th. Things to bring: Refillable water bottle Sneakers Sleeping bag, 
 Pillow, Blankets Rain gear Spare cloths in case we get wet Flashlight 
 Sweater/coat Toothbrush /hairbrush/ toiletries (no showers) sunscreen Bug 
 spray mess kit (you can find them cheap at walmart, or create your own at 
 the dollar store) Plate, bowl, cup silverware 
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC ""-//W3C//DTD HTML 3.2//EN""><BODY><p>Join us for a campout Place to be determined</p> <p>Tenderhearts Require an Parent adult member to be present for all overnights</p> <p>Here is the link for Payment on Zeffy.</p> <p><a href="https://www.zeffy.com/en-US/ticketing/june-campout--2026" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">zeffy.com/en-US/ticketing/june-campout--2026</a></p> <p><b>Payments are due by June 5th.</b></p> <p>Things to bring:</p> <p>Refillable water bottle</p> <p>Sneakers</p> <p>Sleeping bag, Pillow, Blankets</p> <p>Rain gear</p> <p>Spare cloths in case we get wet</p> <p>Flashlight</p> <p>Sweater/coat</p> <p>Toothbrush /hairbrush/ toiletries (no showers)</p> <p>sunscreen</p> <p>Bug spray</p> <p>mess kit (you can find them cheap at walmart, or create your own at the dollar store) Plate, bowl, cup silverware</p> <p></p></BODY></HTML>
